<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8181566>
    dc:description "FIGURE 18. Variability of achene morphology of Calendula. A. C. suffruticosa subsp. monardii (Silveira, Gonçalves &Amirouche 3316, AVE); B. C. suffruticosa subsp. foliosa (Silveira, Gonçalves & Amirouche 3320, AVE); C. C. suffruticosa subsp. djurdjurensis (Silveira, Gonçalves & Amirouche 3321, AVE); D. C. suffruticosa subsp. tunetana (Silveira 3039d, AVE); E. C. suffruticosa subsp. suffruticosa (Silveira 3038, AVE); F. C. arvensis (S. Castro P35 in Silveira 3078, AVE). Rostrate achenes: A1, 2; B1-3; C1, 2; D1-4; E1, 2; F1, 2. Bialate achenes: B4-6. Trialate achenes:A3, 4; C3-5; D5, 6. Cymbiform achenes: E3-5; F3, 4. Vermicular-alate achenes: A5; D7; E6; F5. Vermiculate-exalate achenes: A6, B7, 8; C6, 7; D8; E7 and F6. All achenes in side view, except: A3, B4, B5, C4, D5, E3, E5 and F3 in ventral face view, and B6, C3, C5, D6, E4 and F4 in ± dorsal face view. Scale bars = 1 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8181566/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

